version_description:
This app has been updated by Apple to use the latest Apple signing certificate.

- Optimize the unlock feature;
- Bug fixes & performance improvements.

- Support iPhone X;
- Change App Icon;
- Bug fixes & performance improvements.

Here is a better way to keep your photos secret: Enable the “Decoy Password” feature on app Settings page. The decoy password feature would enter a different set of fake albums, which could hide your real albums.

We will make more great changes on later versions and bring more great features to help our users hiding privacy!
